{"tid":2169452,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"熱血時報黃洋達：張建宗同普遍黃絲，各有各的離地與戇鳩～","createTime":"2020-08-22T13:22:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-22T15:22:05.000Z","uid":271829,"like":1,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"6fa4f057af3d924ce6775955e4d9455a95b5ad5a","tid":2169452,"uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T13:22:11.000Z","msg":"黃洋達：<br />\n張建宗叫大學生去洗碗，當然戇鳩。<br />\n但我見黃絲批評張建宗時，一大堆說法都係類似「做洗碗？點還學貸呀？」、「大學生都去洗碗，邊有咁多碗洗？ 」、「讀完大學做洗碗，連剖房租金都交唔起，畢業慘過未畢業」<br />\n似乎，普遍黃絲，並唔知道洗碗人工係幾撚高！香港地請洗碗工係幾困難！<br />\n各有各的離地與戇鳩～<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6y0Gqn8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6y0Gqn8.jpg&h=0b930b86&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9c0f40f4f3a4ed2a8304c4d62de2fafceb5dd752","tid":2169452,"uid":103230,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T13:24:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sVYPHz1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsVYPHz1.jpg&h=12342aaf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n貼地鳩達<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5bb8dec9ca8fcc50954ce63ff76962edce33a8e","tid":2169452,"uid":34047,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T13:25:06.000Z","msg":"又有邊啲黃絲唔知洗碗難請人<br />\n佢地點解係都要放大一小部分人睇法<br />\n<br />\n例如之前禁食令 九成黃屌政府<br />\n佢地就放大果極少數 話黃絲支持政府乜乜乜<br />\n<br />\n一直啲人屌緊小心健康碼<br />\n然後又話黃絲求仁得仁點點點"},{"pid":"60ce60672c5e29ca64e4c0841f40bfab032d31b9","tid":2169452,"uid":27416,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T13:32:45.000Z","msg":"羊達睇得好透"},{"pid":"8983dcf4c379875de0d0c3b920942d9606abdae3","tid":2169452,"uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9c0f40f4f3a4ed2a8304c4d62de2fafceb5dd752","tid":2169452,"uid":103230,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T13:24:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sVYPHz1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%